{"timestamp":"2026-02-24T08:06:27.254Z","ip":"::1","question":"What happens when an order is created?","answer":"According to the Order Creation process, here are the steps that occur when an order is created:\n\n1. User places order\n2. Order service validates request\n3. Inventory check\n4. Payment processing\n5. Order confirmation\n\nIf any of the following failures occur, the order will be impacted:\n- Payment failure: The order will be failed\n- Inventory unavailable: The order will be rejected","durationMs":1133}
