{"timestamp":"2026-02-24T10:36:05.411Z","ip":"::1","question":"How does shipment work?","answer":"The shipment process involves the following steps:\n\n1. **WMS receives order**: Our Warehouse Management System (WMS) receives the order from the customer.\n2. **Pick and pack happens**: Our team picks the ordered items from the warehouse and packs them for shipping.\n3. **Shipment created**: A shipment is created in our system, which includes the order details and the tracking information.\n4. **Tracking generated**: A tracking number is generated for the shipment, which allows us to track the stat","durationMs":595}
