{"timestamp":"2026-02-24T10:40:16.226Z","ip":"::1","question":"What if payment fails?","answer":"If payment fails, the order will be considered \"failed.\" This is a failure point in the order creation process. \n\n**Order Creation Failure: Payment Failure**\n\n1. Payment processing step fails\n2. Order service flags the order as failed\n3. Order is not confirmed\n4. User is notified of payment failure\n\nNote: Order creation fails, and the order is not processed further.","durationMs":490}
